headline: Airbnb to Participate in the Goldman Sachs Communacopia + Technology Conference
summary: Airbnb, Inc. (NASDAQ: ABNB) announced today that Co-founder and Chief Executive Officer, Brian Chesky, will speak at the Goldman Sachs Communacopia + Technology Conference on Tuesday, September 9, 2025 beginning at 3:05pm PT / 6:05pm ET. A live webcast of the session will be available to the public at https://cc.webcasts.com/gold006/090825a_js/?entity=140_5MW8WXR. A replay will be made available on the Investor Relations website at https://investors.airbnb.com.
